This is it, the climate emergency has hit us like a rock. We're facing an ecological crisis that threatens our very existence, so we must act now. @extinctionrebellion is a global, non-violent direct action group dedicated to turning the tide through civic action and regenerative culture. Join us, #RiseUp @extinctionrebellionnl
